[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=activemq.git;h=72146d2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=activemq.git;h=72146d2&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-8040&quot; title=&quot;KahaDB: PageFile  - Unexpected io error on pagefile write NPE&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AMQ-8040&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AMQ-8040&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - ensure state relating to diskbound tmp file pages is preserved on next update, fix and test&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
